High-Level Design (HLD) — Online Medical Consultation Platform

1. System Overview

The Online Medical Consultation Platform is a cloud-native telemedicine solution that enables patients to book appointments, consult doctors via video calls, make secure payments, and receive realtime notifications.

The system is designed for:

Scalability
High Availability
Realtime Synchronization
Secure Transactions
Collision-Free Appointment Booking

