3. Core Modules
-> Module	Responsibility
-> Authentication Service	User login, session validation, RBAC
-> Appointment Service	Booking management and scheduling
-> Doctor Assignment Engine	Smart doctor allocation
-> Slot Locking Engine	Collision prevention
-> Payment Service	Razorpay integration
-> Video Consultation Service	Jitsi room management
-> Notification Service	Email/push reminders
-> Realtime Sync Service	Firestore listeners
-> Admin Service	Doctor approvals and monitoring

